729106f-a.title: Richmond: Manor Road - Drake Avenue
729106f-a.text:
321 Manor Road, east side, from Drake to Martling Avenues,
showing the Fifty-first Cavalry Brigade Armory. The view is north.
July 7, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
